descp2: True, False or 'auto' (default) Whether the algorithm should be applied to M.T instead of M. The result should approximately be the same. The 'auto' mode will trigger the transposition if M.shape[1] > M.shape[0] since this implementation of randomized SVD tend to be a little faster in that case.
